.SH NAME
spear_smi_wait_till_ready \- wait till flash is ready
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" spear_smi_wait_till_ready
.BI "(struct spear_smi *dev "  ","
.BI "u32 bank "  ","
.BI "unsigned long timeout "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
structure of SMI information.
.IP "bank" 12
flash corresponding to this bank
.IP "timeout" 12
timeout for busy wait condition
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This routine checks for WIP (write in progress) bit in Status register
If successful the routine returns 0 else -EBUSY
